Name: team_size
Description: The number of members in a team

Name: story_points_per_sprint
Description: The number of story points completed per sprint

Name: blocker_severity
Description: The severity level of a blocker

Name: feature_priority
Description: The priority assigned to a feature

Name: velocity
Description: The team's average story points per sprint

Name: sprint_duration
Description: The length of a sprint in days

Name: daily_scrum_duration
Description: The duration of a Daily Scrum in minutes

Name: product_backlog_size
Description: Number of items in the product backlog

Name: feature_documentation_completeness
Description: Percentage of features that are documented

Name: risk_level
Description: Overall risk associated with the project

Name: stakeholder_influence
Description: The level of influence a stakeholder has

Name: sprint_goal_achievement_rate
Description: The percentage of sprint goals achieved

Name: release_plan_features
Description: Number of features included in a release plan

Name: budget
Description: The total budget allocated to the project
